Campus Locations at Saint Louis University

Source: R/stl_tbl_sluPlaces.R
stl_tbl_sluPlaces.Rd

A simple data set containing a few locations on SLU's North Campus.

data(stl_tbl_sluPlaces)

Format

A tibble with 6 rows and 4 variables:

id

record id number

name

location name

lng

longitude (decimal degrees)

lat

latitude (decimal degrees)

Examples

str(stl_tbl_sluPlaces)
#> Classes ‘tbl_df’, ‘tbl’ and 'data.frame':	6 obs. of  4 variables:
